## Python Environment (OpenHands container)

- Use `python3` тАФ never `.venv/bin/python` (venv symlinks are broken inside the sandbox)
- Never use `sudo` for any command тАФ you run as a non-privileged user
- Project root: `/workspace/` (CLI) or `/workspace/{{ name }}/` (Web UI). Run `ls /workspace/` to check.
- Run tests with `python3 -m pytest tests/ -v` (not `pytest` directly)
